00:39:08,066 --> 00:39:09,747
Yes, recruit them immediately.

555
00:39:10,066 --> 00:39:11,226
I feel like an octopus.

556
00:39:11,626 --> 00:39:13,987
If I train a new octopus
with each of my tentacles,

557
00:39:14,626 --> 00:39:15,787
that's 64 new tentacles.

558
00:39:16,546 --> 00:39:18,427
But given Yuehai's current conditions,

559
00:39:18,506 --> 00:39:20,586
I'm afraid those talents
won't want to come here.

560
00:39:20,706 --> 00:39:21,347
Mr. Zheng,

561
00:39:21,626 --> 00:39:23,347
I just called a few schools.

562
00:39:23,626 --> 00:39:26,506
They're all willing to provide us
with technical personnel right away.

563
00:39:27,387 --> 00:39:28,626
You see? Come on!

564
00:39:29,146 --> 00:39:29,907
Ms. Li

565
00:39:30,787 --> 00:39:32,066
- is impressive, right?
