566
00:39:32,066 --> 00:39:33,146
I haven't mentioned it yet.

567
00:39:33,146 --> 00:39:34,387
She's thought about it ahead.

568
00:39:34,867 --> 00:39:36,106
We all should learn from her.

569
00:39:36,226 --> 00:39:37,307
She's the mayor after all.

570
00:39:38,546 --> 00:39:39,480
You are the secretary.

571
00:39:41,186 --> 00:39:41,747
Xie,

572
00:39:42,146 --> 00:39:44,427
are you play-acting
