577
00:39:54,506 --> 00:39:55,006
Really?

578
00:39:57,026 --> 00:39:57,747
Help me down.

579
00:39:58,186 --> 00:40:00,186
Sorry, we're late.

580
00:40:00,747 --> 00:40:01,787
