583
00:40:05,666 --> 00:40:06,666
Thank you.

584
00:40:06,747 --> 00:40:07,247
Thank you.

585
00:40:07,247 --> 00:40:07,747
Come on.

586
00:40:07,747 --> 00:40:09,387
