591
00:40:17,186 --> 00:40:17,787
Got it.

592
00:40:17,827 --> 00:40:18,387
Good.

593
00:40:18,387 --> 00:40:18,887
Come on.

594
00:40:18,947 --> 00:40:19,787
Need a man up here.

595
00:40:20,827 --> 00:40:21,706
(After the typhoon,)

596
00:40:22,026 --> 00:40:24,586
(county relief supplies and aid
arrived promptly.)

597
00:40:25,387 --> 00:40:26,586
(Surprisingly...)

598
00:40:27,907 --> 00:40:28,827
We even have medicine.

599
00:40:54,738 --> 00:40:56,099
