- Yes, cold medicine.

611
00:41:26,787 --> 00:41:27,467
Drink it up.

612
00:41:27,586 --> 00:41:28,387
Warm yourselves up.

613
00:41:28,387 --> 00:41:29,026
Preventative.

614
00:41:29,146 --> 00:41:30,506
Careful, it's a bit hot.

615
00:41:30,546 --> 00:41:31,546
- Okay.
- Slowly.

616
00:41:31,706 --> 00:41:33,146
Come on, have some of this.

617
00:41:33,186 --> 00:41:34,066
Don't catch a cold.

618
00:41:34,066 --> 00:41:34,787
Careful. It's hot.

619
