625
00:42:29,907 --> 00:42:31,907
I heard the typhoon would land here.

626
00:42:31,907 --> 00:42:33,347
So I rushed over.

627
00:42:38,787 --> 00:42:39,467
I'm sorry,

628
00:42:43,907 --> 00:42:44,427
Qiuping,

629
00:42:45,427 --> 00:42:47,352
